name: Tera Patrick
description:
A request of @Dingo00.

This model currently has 2 versions:

Version 1.1 is step 1000. At first I uploaded it as an "early access" version, but, after extensive testing, I've decided it's by far the best and the most accurate one.

Version 1.0 is step 1850. You can also obtain fantastic results with it, I think, but overall I feel her facial features are not as realistic as in 1.1.

Both versions are quite NSFW, I must warn you, though. So, if you don't want Tera flashing her boobs at the earlist opportunity, you might want to add some negative prompt to that effect. :)

You probably know I haven't done many TIs based on pornstars (actually, only one if I'm not mistaken), but Tera Patrick is a special beauty, so she's an exception. This is not an attempt to capture her late 90s looks, though, since there are not many quality pics of that era online (at least that I could find). The pictures I've used for her dataset are more of the mid 2000s to early 2010s era.

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)

modelVersions.name: v1.1
modelVersions.description:
1000-step TI trained on a dataset of 18 images with my usual settings.

At first this was supposed to be the "early access" version of Tera's model, but, after quite intensive testing, I think it's fair to say this version is better than 1.0, so I'm renaming this one and setting it as the main.
